{"tid":1362133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好忘記義士！香港人健忘，但此事絕不能忘！","createTime":"2019-07-24T19:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T19:46:37.000Z","uid":266766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9183e32b510d9dd60197eb72adaed0a4ad2a0e","tid":1362133,"uid":266766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:12:35.000Z","msg":"咁多位義士，你地唔記得咗啦？<br />\n我地爭取緊既野，你地唔記得咗啦？<br />\n已經成日比人話香港人健忘，過兩個月就會無咗件事，肯比翻啲堅持出嚟未啊？<br />\n6.9開始，所有事都不能忘記！<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地唔好再推開花，膠題，帝吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>唔好比人模糊焦點啦！</strong><br />\n36槍呢？元朗呢？上環呢？<br />\n輕鬆咗幾日啦！<br />\n肯翻嚟未？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span></strong><br />\n撤回引渡條例<br />\n釋放被捕人士<br />\n撤回暴動定性<br />\n追究警察濫權<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">727元朗，728上環</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDPWbK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDPWbK2.png&h=f976d142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njVY9wH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnjVY9wH.png&h=712018ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69mJBcN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69mJBcN.png&h=ba77c2ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"400c2669877f7cc278c945bf4029a5484152f684","tid":1362133,"uid":266766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:15:14.000Z","msg":"我錯，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有726機場呀</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836fb8495c6e4ed3f44b1272322f2fa855e6cdcb","tid":1362133,"uid":266766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:17:43.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\